	<div class="title">
		<strong>Welcome to the AWS SDK for PHP</strong>
	</div>
	<p>The AWS SDK for PHP enables developers to build solutions for Amazon Simple Storage Service (Amazon S3), Amazon Elastic Compute Cloud (Amazon EC2), Amazon SimpleDB, and other Amazon services using the PHP programming language. With the SDK, developers can get started in minutes with a single, downloadable package.</p>
	<p>The SDK reference documentation contains detailed information about classes, methods, parameters, properties, constants, inheritance and more. The reference documentation includes working usage examples, a source browser, and XML/JSON representations of the data.</p>

	<br>

